content:
I've download recaf jar file and install JDK 8. When I execute it/start it, it all works fine with <pre><code>java -jar recaf-2.12.0-J8-jar-with-dependencies.jar</code></pre>. I open a class file also no problem. The issue is when I try to edit it is disabled saying:
<pre><code>// =============================================== //
// Recompile disabled. Please run Recaf with a JDK //
// =============================================== //

// Decompiled with: CFR 0.150
...
</code></pre>
Any idea why and how to solve this issue? This is my first time using recaf as well so it might be a newbie question.
